  "content_data": [
    {
      "page_layout": "cover",
      "title": "Case Study",
      "subtitle": "A reusable story arc for before, during, and after transformation",
      "body": "Optimized for customer proof points and business outcomes."
    },
    {
      "page_layout": "content",
      "title": "Challenge",
      "body": [
        "The client faced delivery delay across multiple handoff points.",
        "Decision makers lacked a shared view of progress and blockers.",
        "Teams were over-relying on manual status assembly."
      ],
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "shape",
          "shapeType": "rect",
          "pos": { "x": 5.8, "y": 1.5, "w": 2.8, "h": 2.0 },
          "text": "Before:\nslow, manual,\nhigh friction",
          "style": { "fill": "FEE2E2", "color": "9A3412", "fontSize": 18, "bold": true, "align": "center", "valign": "middle" }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "page_layout": "content",
      "title": "Approach",
      "body": [
        "Built a governed mission flow around repeatable work types.",
        "Introduced template-based outputs for leadership and operations.",
        "Reduced review loops with clearer contracts and validation."
      ],
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "shape",
          "shapeType": "roundRect",
          "pos": { "x": 5.8, "y": 1.6, "w": 2.8, "h": 1.8 },
          "text": "Standardize\nAutomate\nVerify",
          "style": { "fill": "FEF3C7", "color": "92400E", "fontSize": 20, "bold": true, "align": "center", "valign": "middle" }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "page_layout": "content",
      "title": "Outcomes",
      "body": [
        "Cycle time reduced by 62%",
        "Leadership reporting became same-day instead of weekly",
        "Team satisfaction improved with less status admin"
      ],
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "shape",
          "shapeType": "roundRect",
          "pos": { "x": 5.7, "y": 1.5, "w": 1.1, "h": 1.1 },
